title: Complete coverage: Southern Lehigh's Nina DeLuna wins D-11 tennis title over Easton's Elessa Jacobs
text:
By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 13, 2015 3:58 AM, updated October 13, 2015 12:10 PM View/Post Comments 
Southern Lehigh junior Nina DeLuna added another District 11 Class AAA tennis title to her resume on Monday afternoon. 
DeLuna defeated Easton freshman Elessa Jacobs 6-4, 6-2 in the final to clinch her second straight district title.
